These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, rose
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, cabbage
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, sports
2 different pets are kept: pony, frog
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, volleyball
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, taxi
1. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | sprite     | hot-chocolate |
| Flower         | rose  | begonia       |
| Food           | cabbage   | pineapple    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports     | documentary   |
| Pet   | frog      | pony     |
| Sport         | volleyball | swimming      |
| Transport     | taxi       | bus           |

