.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, filmmaking
There 2 different types of food: avocado, strawberry
The people have 2 different jobs:  manager, police-officer
There are 2 different favourite colors: blood-red, blue
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, turkish
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, rock
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, van
1. the person who likes blood-red is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of rock is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
3. the person who likes blue is in an odd position##4
4. the turkish is on the left of the manager##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| Hobby      | filmmaking         | dancing       |
| Food          | avocado        | strawberry |
| Job           | police-officer | manager    |
| Color   | blue        | blood-red  |
| Nationality   | turkish        | thai       |
| Music-Genre           | rock            | folk        |
| Transport     | van            | ship       |

