.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-4::.
City: paris, venice
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, video-games
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, sports
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, soul
There are 2 different favourite colors: chestnut, apricot
There 2 different types of food: garlic, papaya
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, van
1. the fan of r&b is in an even position##4
2. the person eating papaya is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
4. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating papaya is the person watching action movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| City      | venice    | paris   |
| Hobby         | video-games | card-games |
| Movie-Genre   | sports      | action     |
| Music-Genre   | soul        | r&b        |
| Color           | chestnut        | apricot |
| Food         | garlic    | papaya |
| Transport     | van         | boat       |

